name: AIR Supplements/ 90 Capsules
description:
90 Capsules 

Each ocean capsule contains: 500mg of GlycOmega-PLUS, Green Lipped Mussel and encapsulating materials.

No artificial flavors, colors or preservatives.

Store away from heat in a dry place. 

Recommended dosage: Take up to 2 capsules daily, during the morning and evening with meals.

name: AIR Cream/ 30 ml 1oz.
description:
Active Instant Relief Cream 

30 ml/ 1 oz. 

Ingredients: Green Lipped Mussel Extract (GlycOmega-Plus), Glucosamine Sulfate, Chondroitin Sulphate, Omega 3 Oil, Menthol, Jojoba Oil, Shea Butter, Ginger Oil, Tea Tree Oil, Capsicum Oil, Eucalyptus Oil. 

Directions: Use liberally as needed and massage in until absorbed.

Caution: Cream and Supplements are not recommended for people who are allergic to shellfish or pregnant or breastfeeding. 
Keep away from eyes.
